Notes: WIAC Tournament - First Round...UWO advances to play at UW-Eau Claire (16-9)
in the semifinals on Friday (Feb. 27)...UWW ends 2015 season after appearing
in the NCAA Div. III Final Four the previous two years...UWO and UWW split two
games during the regular season...UWO ends game with 20-5 scoring run.
